features:
  - 6 parallel grain-producing streams
  - 6 voice polyphony with ASDR
  - per-stream parameters covering rhythmic division, envelope, tuning, panning, offset, size, probability, and gain
  - per-stream LFO and random sample-and-hold oscillators for automating stream parameters
  - global drive and reverb for coloration
  - sample-accurate timing
