<p>
  <a :href="$data.liveUrl" target="_blank">moire</a> is a granular synthesizer
  for building sound through layered polyrhythmic sampling.
</p>

<p>
  It provides independently controlled streams that each generate grains at
  integral subdivisions of the clock. Parameters can be automated with
  per-stream modulation sources.
</p>

